snippet.title: Miszou: A Lofi Rollerblading Game | Official Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Back the Kickstarter Here:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/voyagerstudio/miszou-a-lofi-rollerblading-game

This is the Kickstarter campaign trailer for our Lofi-inspired Rollerblading game: Miszou. Skate, Grind, and flip your way through the vibrant world turtles of Miszou while also meeting a colourful cast of characters along the way!

Miszou is an indie game developed by us. We’ve been working on it for almost a year now and we are working hard to push it out. If you support our Kickstarter or even watch our devlogs that means so much to us. Thank you everyone!

Follow us on Social Media! 
https://www.instagram.com/voyagergamestudio/
https://www.tiktok.com/@voyagerstudio
https://twitter.com/Voyager_Studio

Join our Community! 
https://discord.gg/RXUX96CDXs
